---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="Michelle's SHIT" description="FUCK OVERRATED HEADPHONES..." />
	</head>
	<body>
		<script is:inline src="/warning.js"></script>
		<Header />
		
		<main>
			<section class="hero mc-border">
				<img src="/blog/contents/bestpair.png" alt="Beyerdynamic DT 770 Pro Headphone" style="display: block; margin: 0 auto 15px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: 500px;">
				<div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 25px;">
					<a href="/blog" class="mc-btn" style="font-size: 1.5rem; padding: 15px 40px; background: var(--pink-neon); color: white; display: inline-block; text-shadow: 2px 2px 0 #000;">
						<i class="fa-solid fa-book"></i> VISIT MY BLOG!
					</a>
				</div>
				<h1>DT 770 PRO AND AIRPODS PRO 2 ARE THE BEST PAIRS OF HEADPHONES TOGETHER</h1>
				<p class="subtitle">FUCK OVERHYPED HEADPHONES, AIRPODS PRO 2 IS THE REAL HEADPHONES PAIR (IF YOU WEAR IT TOGETHER).</p>
				<p class="subtitle">Seriously though! It is by far the most well-rounded over-ears headphone without compromise, maybe not the sound. The build really is the classic Beyedynanic build, cheap looking but rugged in a good way. This means this headphone wouldn't just die or get scratched whenever you accidentally dropped or bumped it. Although the sound is rather bad, you can EQ it if you have the mental clarity, sanity, and capacity to make it better than HD 800S. </p>
				<p class="subtitle">So bad sound but comfy earpads? JUST WEAR THEM OVER THE OTHER. </p>
				<p class="subtitle">Airpods Pro 2 good sound and ANC will be helped by DT 770 PRO's excellent high frequency attenuation</p>
				<p class="subtitle">Just buy Airpods Pro 2 for your sanity, please. They sound better.</p>
				
				<div style="margin-top: 30px;">
					<a href="https://www.amazon.com/Apple-Generation-Cancelling-Transparency-Personalized/dp/B0CHWRXH8B" target="_blank" class="mc-btn" style="background: #FF9900; color: #000; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 10px;">
						<i class="fa-brands fa-amazon" style="font-size: 1.4rem;"></i>
						<span>Buy on Amazon</span>
					</a>
				</div>
				<div style="margin-top:20px;">
					<span style="font-size:3rem; animation: float 2s infinite;">💖</span>
				</div>
			</section>        
		</main>

		<Footer />        
	</body>
</html>